First day.

1069
00:57:26,782 --> 00:57:27,908
Well, how'd it go?

1070
00:57:27,983 --> 00:57:30,144
I mean, is Lorenzo behaving himself?

1071
00:57:30,219 --> 00:57:30,947
It went great, man.

1072
00:57:31,020 --> 00:57:33,750
I collected on nine different accounts.

1073
00:57:33,823 --> 00:57:34,881
I did 12.

1074
00:57:34,957 --> 00:57:36,015
Wait, wait, wait a minute.

1075
00:57:36,091 --> 00:57:40,528
You got 12 different
clients to pay their bills?

1076
00:57:40,596 --> 00:57:43,121
Yeah, that's right.

1077
00:57:43,199 --> 00:57:44,461
You got nine?

1078
00:57:44,533 --> 00:57:46,797
Yes, sir.

1079
00:57:46,869 --> 00:57:48,996
And you?

1080
00:57:49,071 --> 00:57:50,629
Over 20.

1081
00:57:50,706 --> 00:57:54,164
Ha, ha, ha!

1082
00:57:54,243 --> 00:57:58,737
