1106
00:58:55,547 --> 00:58:57,037
- You look familiar.
- Well, whatever.

1107
00:58:57,316 --> 00:58:58,374
Scoot over.

1108
00:58:58,450 --> 00:58:59,576
(male) Come on have a seat, man.

1109
00:58:59,651 --> 00:59:00,675
Deal me in.

1110
00:59:00,752 --> 00:59:04,415
(male) Off with the dresses
and on with the suits.

1111
00:59:04,489 --> 00:59:06,787
Oh, yeah.

1112
00:59:06,858 --> 00:59:10,021
(Frankie) All right, fellas,
all right, fellas, here we go.

1113
00:59:10,095 --> 00:59:12,996
(male) Shoe shine, shoe shine,
come on buff 'em up.

1114
00:59:13,065 --> 00:59:15,795
Shine 'em up.

1115
00:59:20,472 --> 00:59:23,305
I see that 50 and I'll raise you 100.

1116
00:59:23,375 --> 00:59:27,402
Come on, come on, the inhale
to the exhale all day long.

1117
00:59:27,479 --> 00:59:29,811
(Lorenzo) I got it right here, man.

1118
00:59:29,881 --> 00:59:31,712
(Frankie)
You stiff now, getting stiff, fellas.

1119
00:59:31,783 --> 00:59:34,547
(male) Ain't no time for
tremblin' now, gentlemen.

1120
00:59:34,619 --> 00:59:37,417
(Lorenzo) Come on, put it in, put it in.

1121
00:59:37,489 --> 00:59:39,320
I'm out.

1122
00:59:39,391 --> 00:59:42,019
(Lorenzo) There we are, gentlemen.

1123
00:59:42,094 --> 00:59:43,391
Thank you very much.

1124
00:59:43,462 --> 00:59:44,724
Thank you. Thank you.

1125
00:59:44,796 --> 00:59:45,922
(Frankie) Don't get too lucky, Lorenzo.

1126
00:59:45,997 --> 00:59:46,986
Why?

1127
00:59:47,065 --> 00:59:49,431
(Frankie) You gonna guard your money
or you gonna deal?

1128
00:59:49,501 --> 00:59:50,627
I'll deal. I'll deal.

1129
00:59:50,702 --> 00:59:51,794
(male) Don't let it go to your head.

1130
00:59:51,870 --> 00:59:56,671
(male) Man, the name might change,
but the game is still the same.

1131
00:59:56,742 --> 01:00:00,007
(Lorenzo) What am I gonna do
with all this money?

1132
01:00:00,078 --> 01:00:02,842
I have no idea.

1133
01:00:02,914 --> 01:00:09,547
(Lorenzo) I think I'll buy me an island
somewhere off the map.

1134
01:00:12,524 --> 01:00:19,828
(Frankie) Okay, I'm gonna see that
500 and raise you 2 grand.

1135
01:00:24,469 --> 01:00:30,533
I'll see that and raise you 3 grand.

1136
01:00:30,609 --> 01:00:32,406
(male) Gettin' to be some crazy money.

1137
01:00:32,477 --> 01:00:33,967
And change.

1138
01:00:34,045 --> 01:00:35,979
[laughing] Ha-ha-ha-ha-ha!

1139
01:00:36,047 --> 01:00:41,713
Lorenzo, Lorenzo, always the optimist.

1140
01:00:41,787 --> 01:00:44,017
I call.

1141
01:00:44,089 --> 01:00:47,718
There you go.

1142
01:00:47,793 --> 01:00:49,158
(Frankie) Read 'em and weep.

1143
01:00:49,428 --> 01:00:53,524
Full house beats a straight.

1144
01:00:53,598 --> 01:00:56,465
Thanks for stopping by though,
and I'll see you

1145
01:00:56,535 --> 01:00:58,059
in less than 2 weeks.

1146
01:00:58,136 --> 01:00:59,535
Don't be late.

1147
01:00:59,604 --> 01:01:02,732
And whatever you do, don't be short.

1148
01:01:03,175 --> 01:01:05,609
(male)
You got a card up your sleeve, sucker.

1149
01:01:05,677 --> 01:01:07,406
Easy guys. Calm down.

1150
01:01:07,479 --> 01:01:08,104
Ta bien. Ta bien.

1151
01:01:08,180 --> 01:01:09,807
(male) Let's be easy, gentlemen.

1152
01:01:09,881 --> 01:01:12,679
Why don't you get your hands
off me, and we'll inspect

1153
01:01:12,751 --> 01:01:16,050
my wardrobe in a more
gentlemanly fashion.

1154
01:01:16,121 --> 01:01:18,885
Carmine, help me w'my coat.

1155
01:01:33,038 --> 01:01:34,801
Good night, gentlemen.

1156
01:01:34,873 --> 01:01:38,138
Now how we gonna leave this?

1157
01:01:41,713 --> 01:01:42,975
I'm outta here.

1158
01:01:43,048 --> 01:01:44,208
Yeah, good riddance.

