- I'm in.

1164
01:02:01,600 --> 01:02:02,760
(Lorenzo) Where are we going?

1165
01:02:02,835 --> 01:02:04,325
(Omar) We're going home.

1166
01:02:04,403 --> 01:02:06,064
I don't want to go home.

1167
01:02:06,339 --> 01:02:07,829
You need to sleep it off.

1168
01:02:07,907 --> 01:02:11,308
I need to die, tonight.

1169
01:02:11,377 --> 01:02:13,538
Would you kill me please?

1170
01:02:13,612 --> 01:02:16,012
'Cause I'm drunk.

1171
01:02:16,082 --> 01:02:17,481
Come on.

1172
01:02:17,550 --> 01:02:19,745
I'm by a riverside.

1173
01:02:19,819 --> 01:02:25,553
Put me in a plastic bag
just like a pussy cat.

1174
01:02:25,624 --> 01:02:29,720
Throw me in, just like
I tried to do to you.

1175
01:02:29,795 --> 01:02:33,458
I know. Let's go home.

1176
01:02:40,506 --> 01:02:43,407
You know what Hell is?

1177
01:02:43,476 --> 01:02:45,740
Hell is other people.

1178
01:02:51,484 --> 01:02:53,349
[knocking on door]

1179
01:02:53,419 --> 01:02:54,818
Come in.

1180
01:02:54,887 --> 01:02:56,616
You wanted to see me, sir?

1181
01:02:56,689 --> 01:02:59,715
Yeah, come in and shut the door.

1182
01:03:02,995 --> 01:03:04,690
I just got a telegram from Stan.

1183
01:03:04,764 --> 01:03:08,757
We're authorized to offer
30 cents on the dollar.

1184
01:03:08,834 --> 01:03:11,098
Thirty cents on the dollar?

1185
01:03:11,170 --> 01:03:13,001
Twenty cents on the dollar
if the client comes

1186
01:03:13,072 --> 01:03:15,905
into the office in person and pays cash.

1187
01:03:15,975 --> 01:03:17,966
Wow, that's something.

1188
01:03:18,043 --> 01:03:19,374
Yeah.

1189
01:03:19,445 --> 01:03:21,106
Stan wants all the hospital
accounts wrapped up

1190
01:03:21,180 --> 01:03:22,670
before he gets back.

1191
01:03:22,748 --> 01:03:24,511
Must be having a great time.

1192
01:03:24,583 --> 01:03:27,518
That or the sun went
through his head, right?

1193
01:03:30,556 --> 01:03:31,818
I'm sorry.

1194
01:03:31,891 --> 01:03:34,018
I need every hand on deck.

1195
01:03:34,093 --> 01:03:36,823
Aye-aye, sir.

1196
01:03:45,871 --> 01:03:50,433
(Lorenzo) Because of eminent deadlines,
over which I have no control,

1197
01:03:50,509 --> 01:03:52,568
starting today we're gonna
split you into two groups

1198
01:03:52,645 --> 01:03:55,808
and extend the workday to
12 hours for each group.

1199
01:03:55,881 --> 01:03:57,109
We'll man the phones around the clock

1200
01:03:57,183 --> 01:03:58,844
'til every account is settled.

1201
01:03:58,918 --> 01:04:00,909
We'll fight them on the seas
and in the oceans.

1202
01:04:00,986 --> 01:04:02,977
We'll fight them on the fields
and on the hills.

1203
01:04:03,055 --> 01:04:05,888
I ain't working more than 8 hours.

1204
01:04:05,958 --> 01:04:07,050
Who said that?

1205
01:04:07,126 --> 01:04:08,150
God bless you, Lorenzo.

1206
01:04:08,227 --> 01:04:09,455
(Lorenzo) I make the rules here, sailor.

1207
01:04:09,528 --> 01:04:12,019
Get in line or go home.

1208
01:04:12,097 --> 01:04:14,930
Now, who wants to work the day shift?

1209
01:04:15,000 --> 01:04:16,092
Who wants to work the night shift?

1210
01:04:16,168 --> 01:04:19,001
It makes no difference to me
because I'm gonna be here 24/7,

1211
01:04:19,071 --> 01:04:21,631
leading the invasion.

1212
01:04:22,908 --> 01:04:24,967
He got to be crazy.

1213
01:04:25,044 --> 01:04:28,536
I know the check better clear.

1214
01:04:28,614 --> 01:04:31,447
Could you please hold, sir?

1215
01:04:31,517 --> 01:04:34,008
I'll see what we can do.

1216
01:04:35,654 --> 01:04:40,591
♪♪♪

1217
01:04:45,970 --> 01:04:47,665
I see that you have
an outstanding balance

1218
01:04:47,738 --> 01:04:53,506
of $1,972.33.

1219
01:04:55,079 --> 01:04:56,637
Yes, no, not you.

1220
01:04:56,714 --> 01:04:59,274
No, he is.

