the table on a roar?"

1291
01:13:18,030 --> 01:13:19,497
(Lorenzo) Yeah, that's it.

1292
01:13:19,565 --> 01:13:22,557
Well, I wish you guys
all the luck in the world.

1293
01:13:22,635 --> 01:13:26,731
It's been quite a ride.

1294
01:13:26,806 --> 01:13:29,775
Iggy, let's pass out the dolls.

