of a village blacksmith.

1410
01:21:27,840 --> 01:21:31,571
"His brow is wet with honest sweat.

1411
01:21:31,644 --> 01:21:35,205
"He earns whatever he can
and looks the whole world

1412
01:21:35,281 --> 01:21:41,481
