1413
01:21:41,554 --> 01:21:44,580
I did a bit of teaching in my day.

1414
01:21:44,657 --> 01:21:47,888
Mr. James, that's wonderful news, sir.

1415
01:21:47,961 --> 01:21:52,261
I'll just make a note you're
paying your debt in full.

1416
01:21:52,332 --> 01:21:53,663
Thank you, sir.

