1430
01:23:01,034 --> 01:23:03,969
Yes, sir.

1431
01:23:04,037 --> 01:23:07,302
This is unbelievable.

1432
01:23:07,373 --> 01:23:09,637
Your folks, they come from skid row?

1433
01:23:09,709 --> 01:23:12,439
Some of them do.

1434
01:23:12,512 --> 01:23:14,844
(Stan) Well, they just set an
all-time collections record

1435
01:23:14,914 --> 01:23:16,711
at Lump Sum.

1436
01:23:16,783 --> 01:23:18,978
I don't know how they managed
to get results like this,

1437
01:23:19,052 --> 01:23:23,489
once Lorenzo left the scene,
but seeing is believing

1438
01:23:23,556 --> 01:23:25,922
and I'd like to offer 'em
full-time employment.

1439
01:23:25,992 --> 01:23:27,459
Fantastic.

1440
01:23:27,527 --> 01:23:30,860
And also pay 'em for the training period

1441
01:23:30,930 --> 01:23:32,830
they endured under Mr. Adams.

1442
01:23:32,899 --> 01:23:35,424
(Pastor Kevin)
Thank you so much, Mr. Davenport.

1443
01:23:35,501 --> 01:23:38,402
(Stan)
I left this company in your hands.

1444
01:23:38,471 --> 01:23:40,701
I trusted you.

1445
01:23:40,773 --> 01:23:43,970
And you let me down completely.

1446
01:23:44,043 --> 01:23:48,639
I have no choice but to press charges.

1447
01:23:48,715 --> 01:23:51,775
Don't you have anything
to say for yourself?

1448
01:23:51,851 --> 01:23:54,081
Nothing?

1449
01:23:54,354 --> 01:23:55,616
What can I say?

1450
