I want that $12,000 you lost
at the poker game.

1457
01:24:29,555 --> 01:24:31,819
And if I see you within
a hundred yards of this office

1458
01:24:31,891 --> 01:24:34,792
ever again, you're gonna be on
your way to jail so fast

1459
