like the terminator.

1466
01:24:50,576 --> 01:24:53,374
You need to talk to him, man.

1467
01:24:53,446 --> 01:24:55,505
I don't work here anymore.

1468
01:24:55,581 --> 01:24:58,709
Say what?

1469
01:24:58,785 --> 01:25:00,548
I hope you understand,
it's not that I don't think

1470
01:25:00,620 --> 01:25:01,746
