1471
01:25:01,821 --> 01:25:05,279
I just need a couple more weeks
to find out for myself.

1472
01:25:05,358 --> 01:25:08,759
In the meantime, I guarantee
minimum wage and commission.

1473
01:25:08,828 --> 01:25:12,389
It's always best to reward
performance, you know?

1474
01:25:12,465 --> 01:25:16,026
Pastor? Pastor?

1475
01:25:16,102 --> 01:25:19,868
Oh, I'm sure that will
be fine, Mr. Davenport.

1476
01:25:19,939 --> 01:25:23,602
(Pastor Kevin)
Lorenzo, hold on. Where you going?

1477
01:25:23,676 --> 01:25:24,768
I didn't get a chance--

1478
01:25:24,800 --> 01:25:25,960
To say good-bye?

1479
01:25:26,035 --> 01:25:27,263
No, come on.

1480
01:25:27,336 --> 01:25:28,997
I want you to come by the LEC later.

1481
01:25:29,071 --> 01:25:31,699
We have a Bible study
every Wednesday night.

1482
01:25:31,774 --> 01:25:33,742
I don't think so, Pastor.

1483
01:25:33,809 --> 01:25:36,869
You seem like a nice guy,
and I appreciate all you tried

1484
01:25:36,945 --> 01:25:40,381
