don't change his stripes.

1485
01:25:40,449 --> 01:25:41,609
You know what I mean?

1486
01:25:41,684 --> 01:25:45,051
I am what I am, and I always will be.

1487
01:25:45,321 --> 01:25:47,050
You're gonna pay back Stan, right?

1488
01:25:47,323 --> 01:25:48,483
I'm gonna try.

1489
01:25:48,557 --> 01:25:49,751
You really mean that?

1490
01:25:49,825 --> 01:25:51,003
Yeah.

1491
01:25:51,301 --> 01:25:52,859
Well, I rest my case.

1492
01:25:52,936 --> 01:25:58,499
Lorenzo, you have a lot to offer
the world, and God is a giver

1493
01:25:58,575 --> 01:26:02,511
and he wants us to be givers too.

1494
01:26:02,579 --> 01:26:06,515
Let me give you some advice, Pastor.

1495
01:26:06,583 --> 01:26:09,780
Don't waste your time on lost causes.

1496
01:26:13,957 --> 01:26:20,920
Lorenzo, I invest my time
and my life in lost causes.

1497
01:26:21,198 --> 01:26:23,860
(Alex) The way I see it, Lorenzo,
maybe you meant

1498
01:26:23,934 --> 01:26:27,233
to take advantage of us,
or maybe you didn't.

1499
01:26:27,304 --> 01:26:28,703
I don't know.

1500
01:26:28,772 --> 01:26:33,436
But I do know through you, God
has given me a second chance,

1501
01:26:33,510 --> 01:26:35,603
and I just want to thank you, man.

1502
01:26:35,679 --> 01:26:36,941
Me too, Lorenzo.

1503
01:26:37,214 --> 01:26:38,738
Me three, boss.

1504
01:26:38,815 --> 01:26:41,909
(Kasheera)
We love you, Lorenzo. We all do.

1505
01:26:41,985 --> 01:26:44,249
Every one of us knows how
I feel to get caught

1506
01:26:44,321 --> 01:26:45,948
in a situation that you just can't seem

1507
01:26:46,223 --> 01:26:48,316
to get out of, don't we?

1508
01:26:48,391 --> 01:26:49,551
Yes, we do.

1509
01:26:49,626 --> 01:26:51,218
We don't judge you, Lorenzo.

1510
01:26:51,294 --> 01:26:52,784
You're a hero to us.

1511
01:26:52,862 --> 01:26:54,591
