there's something I'd like to say.

1515
01:27:07,644 --> 01:27:15,244
It's been a long time since
I've been able to help anyone.

1516
01:27:18,388 --> 01:27:25,590
It's been a long time, still,
since I've wanted

1517
01:27:25,662 --> 01:27:28,927
to help anyone.

1518
01:27:32,535 --> 01:27:35,470
But things are different now.

1519
01:27:35,538 --> 01:27:40,407
Things are changing.
My life is changing.

1520
01:27:40,477 --> 01:27:45,414
And I have my own lodgings now,
and I have a spare room,

1521
01:27:45,482 --> 01:27:47,575
Lorenzo.

1522
01:27:47,651 --> 01:27:50,814
It's for you anytime you need it.

1523
01:27:50,887 --> 01:27:52,718
And I'm building up my library again.

1524
01:27:52,789 --> 01:27:57,749
I have some first-edition books
you might like to read.

1525
01:28:02,932 --> 01:28:04,923
Wednesday night?

1526
01:28:05,001 --> 01:28:06,866
Wednesday night, son.

1527
01:28:06,936 --> 01:28:10,030
Choir rehearsal is Tuesday.

1528
01:28:34,764 --> 01:28:37,699
Bob, Johnny.

1529
01:28:42,005 --> 01:28:44,337
I'm sorry.

1530
01:28:44,407 --> 01:28:46,307
Sorry?

1531
01:28:46,376 --> 01:28:49,903
Yeah, you're sorry all right.

1532
01:28:49,979 --> 01:28:53,471
Maybe, I'll never make it up
to you or the others,

1533
01:28:53,550 --> 01:29:00,353
but if I can make it
right someday, I will.

1534
01:29:06,796 --> 01:29:10,357
Yeah, my number's unlisted.

1535
01:29:10,433 --> 01:29:13,095
It's kind of touching in a way.

1536
